  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The 16 external interrupts, EXINT[15:0], are driven into the SCR from the ports"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Below SCR pins are multiplexed to an External interrupt [15:0] Pin Functions and we can select the pin through MODPISEL register"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "P00.0 to P00.3",
        "P01.0 to P01.3"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Other pins have exclusive External Interrupt Input pin functions"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "P00.4 to P00.7",
        "P01.4 to P01.4"
      ]
    },
